 <span data-ttu-id="ac74a-234"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> 支持从以下类进行隐式转换：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac74a-234"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> supports implicit conversions from the following classes:</span></span>  
  
