 <span data-ttu-id="ac74a-235">此方法接受上面列出的参数的对象 `builder` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac74a-235">This method accepts the objects listed above for the `builder` parameter.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac74a-236">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> 和 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> 运算符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac74a-236">For more information, see the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Implicit%2A> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder.op_Addition%2A> operators.</span></span>  
  
