## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ac74a-298">`key` 添加到当前元素序列的末尾。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ac74a-298">`key` is added to the end of the current sequence of elements.</span></span>  
  
